title: Seeing Warwick Castle from only the outside - Warwick
author: kware17
text:
I am heading up to Stratford-upon-avon from London for the day next weekend. I want to swing by Warwick Castle . I know that the entrance fee is 20GBP, but I wanted to see if I would be able to see anything from the outside without having to go into the Castle?
